Doke-Purpose: Ingest Doke runtime language, timezone, geolocation, and proxy alignment metadata.
Doke-Subsystem: chrome/app startup command-line handling.
Doke-Detection-Target: BrowserScan, CreepJS, and location/timezone/proxy consistency checks.
Doke-Rollback: Remove this patch from patches/chromium/series and rebuild Chromium; DokeBrowser will keep writing alignment metadata but Chromium will ignore it.

diff --git a/chrome/app/chrome_main.cc b/chrome/app/chrome_main.cc
--- a/chrome/app/chrome_main.cc
